                     <interp inst="t18290910-24-person328" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I have a piece of silk, pawned with me on the 26th of July, by Wilks, as I believe - this is the duplicate I gave.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18290910-24-person329">
                  JOHN 
                  WILLIAM ANDREWS
               <interp inst="t18290910-24-person329" type="surname" value="WILLIAM ANDREWS"></interp>
