               <p>(Property produced and sworn to.)</p>
               <p>WILKS - <rs id="t18290910-24-verdict137" type="verdictDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18290910-24-verdict137" type="verdictCategory" value="guilty"></interp>
               GUILTY
            </rs>. Aged 19.</p>





